{"tid":1369743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"認認真真，元朗半天遊大家一齊放鬆下啦","createTime":"2019-07-26T18:52:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T04:32:09.000Z","uid":257961,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"04155e66394414a352661d72fe354e7e3dc1685c","tid":1369743,"uid":257961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:52:10.000Z","msg":"近排心情唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，想到郊外呼吸清新空氣， 有意搞個元朗半天遊<br />\n<br />\n大概行程會係去：<br />\n元朗大街買下恆香老婆餅<br />\n掃下街邊小食 例如炸蠔餅<br />\n勝利牛丸 天奴豬排 永年車仔麵 B仔涼粉<br />\n之後會去偉大既中共前總理李鵬既追思會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再去yoho shopping mall 行街<br />\n如果各位手足有其他建議可以再商討<br />\n<br />\n人數預唔多，唔超過10人到<br />\n不過個行程有風險， 就係要小心牛隻或者野豬襲擊 大家自備應該要既物品<br />\n響應政府呼籲，本此活動不會去或參加任何示威活動，希望手足注意⚠️及勇躍參加！"},{"pid":"b4d5d5ccc4761f1e76fb2e5b8e90e138fbce95d8","tid":1369743,"uid":257961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T19:56:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7a9d470717e50eeed65e8ce00b73304cc8bb0d44","tid":1369743,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T20:00:00.000Z","msg":"唔超過3人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d91e734e22766910a37cd0a9ed4cc2c63e9f5669","tid":1369743,"uid":222362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T20:04:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sHj7zKh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsHj7zKh.png&h=243581ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5db19438a1bf74882de45c9ec795c5513bf4a2a","tid":1369743,"uid":257961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T04:32:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}